  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "HR & Admin Executive",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Job Description:</strong></em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage the full recruitment process, including analyzing job needs, choosing recruitment channels, posting jobs, screening resumes, conducting phone and on-site interviews, performing background checks, and negotiating offers to hire top talent.</li>\n  <li>Expand recruitment channels, simplify the hiring process, and improve recruitment efficiency.</li>\n  <li>Work with departments to understand their hiring needs and develop suitable recruitment plans.</li>\n  <li>Handle employee processes like onboarding, probation, transfers, promotions, and resignations, ensuring they follow legal and regulatory rules.</li>\n  <li>Assist in creating performance evaluation systems, collecting results, and supporting employee growth.</li>\n  <li>Help develop, improve, and update HR policies and procedures.</li>\n  <li>Ensure HR practices comply with Singapore laws and are reviewed and updated regularly.</li>\n  <li>Take care of daily office tasks like buying supplies, maintaining equipment, and managing files.</li>\n  <li>Help organize company events and meetings.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>3 years of HR experience, with understanding of Singapore HR regulations, processes, and the Employment Act.</li>\n  <li>Experienced in recruitment and interviewing, and knowledgeable about various hiring approaches.</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication, teamwork, and problem-solving skills.</li>\n  <li>Well-organized, good at time management, and capable of handling multiple tasks effectively.</li>\n  <li>Fast learner with a self-driven attitude.</li>\n  <li>Positive, sports enthusiast, team-oriented, and able to perform under pressure.</li>\n  <li>Background in the technology industry is an advantage.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
